OL,7,FTelevision veteran Dr Samir Shah has
OL,8,Fbeen appointed as the new BBC chairman
OL,9,Fmonths after the former head of the
OL,10,Fbroadcaster resigned.
OL,12,FDr Shah has been celebrated for his
OL,13,Fwork championing diversity and last
OL,14,Fworked at the corporation in 1998.
OL,16,FThe BBC has been without a chairman
OL,17,Fsince June after Richard Sharp
OL,18,Ffinished his time in the role
OL,19,Ffollowing his resignation in April.
